Give it to me, give it to me.

264
00:22:51,759 --> 00:22:55,495
Sir, this is a magical
couple's watch, look.

265
00:22:55,519 --> 00:22:59,856
When one watch adjusts the time,
the other watch's hands will also move.

266
00:22:59,880 --> 00:23:03,095
Even when separated by thousands
of miles, they can synchronize.

267
00:23:03,119 --> 00:23:04,919
It's amazing, right?

268
00:23:10,400 --> 00:23:13,200
Really, take a look.

269
00:23:17,640 --> 00:23:20,440
He doesn't like it, thank you.

270
00:23:24,200 --> 00:23:25,177
Who likes you?

271
00:23:25,201 --> 00:23:27,095
- You.
- How do you feel that?

272
00:23:27,119 --> 00:23:28,919
Look at your hand.

273
00:23:31,160 --> 00:23:33,255
Wait, I'm going to the bathroom.

274
00:23:33,279 --> 00:23:35,559
Sure, go ahead.

275
00:23:41,839 --> 00:23:43,639
Isn't bathroom...

276
00:23:53,119 --> 00:23:58,000
Just say you want to buy the
watch. Why use such a cliché excuse?

277
00:24:04,400 --> 00:24:05,856
You are back, huh?

278
00:24:05,880 --> 00:24:07,680
Let's go.

279
00:24:10,240 --> 00:24:12,040
What's wrong?

280
00:24:12,960 --> 00:24:15,416
You just went to bathroom.

281
00:24:15,440 --> 00:24:17,240
What else?

282
00:24:18,920 --> 00:24:21,575
Let's go, I'll buy you a coat.

283
00:24:21,599 --> 00:24:23,399
Let's go.

284
00:24:35,920 --> 00:24:37,720
You bought it!

285
00:24:40,160 --> 00:24:41,856
How did you put it on me?

286
00:24:41,880 --> 00:24:43,880
Only you know the tricks?

287
00:24:43,904 --> 00:24:45,960
♫ Set off ♫

288
00:24:47,119 --> 00:24:48,696
You'd buy me clothes.

289
00:24:48,720 --> 00:24:49,735
Yes.

290
00:24:49,759 --> 00:24:52,599
Go.

291
00:24:56,200 --> 00:24:59,319
Today I must exhaust his energy.

292
00:25:00,483 --> 00:25:03,095
♫ Are they waiting for an answer ♫

293
00:25:03,119 --> 00:25:07,936
Wouldn't you buy me clothes? What's
the meaning of bringing me here?

294
00:25:07,960 --> 00:25:11,919
First, let's exercise. Open both hands.

295
00:25:14,784 --> 00:25:17,936
♫ Spring grows, summer extends ♫

296
00:25:17,960 --> 00:25:19,255
Inhale.

297
00:25:19,279 --> 00:25:21,735
♫ Blooming freely ♫

298
00:25:21,759 --> 00:25:24,376
Exhale.

299
00:25:24,400 --> 00:25:26,760
Okay, warm up.

300
00:25:28,617 --> 00:25:31,912
♫ Autumn harvest, winter storage ♫

301
00:25:31,936 --> 00:25:34,834
♫ Season changes ♫

302
00:25:34,858 --> 00:25:36,950
♫ With you ♫

303
00:25:41,160 --> 00:25:44,535
Fine, wait and see.

304
00:25:44,559 --> 00:25:47,735
You swim twenty laps first.

305
00:25:47,759 --> 00:25:49,559
Okay.

306
00:25:59,599 --> 00:26:00,576
Let me hold you now.

307
00:26:00,600 --> 00:26:03,296
What-What are you doing?

308
00:26:06,176 --> 00:26:07,976
Someone is watching.

309
00:26:08,000 --> 00:26:10,919
I know, I just want to be close to you.

310
00:26:13,039 --> 00:26:14,976
Before, Yue...

311
00:26:15,000 --> 00:26:16,800
What?

312
00:26:19,680 --> 00:26:22,735
I find you're not serious now.

313
00:26:22,759 --> 00:26:24,815
Never been serious.

314
00:26:24,839 --> 00:26:26,680
Let go, let go!

315
00:26:33,960 --> 00:26:35,760
Wu Suo Wei!

316
00:26:59,039 --> 00:27:05,720
Wu Suo Wei! Wu Suo Wei! Wu Suo Wei!

317
00:27:36,440 --> 00:27:38,896
Hello, has it arrived already?

318
00:27:38,920 --> 00:27:44,480
Alright, alright, I'll go back now.

319
00:27:45,880 --> 00:27:47,456
Okay.

320
00:27:47,480 --> 00:27:49,176
Let's go.

321
00:27:49,200 --> 00:27:52,176
Go to the company, I'll tell you later.

322
00:27:52,200 --> 00:27:53,815
Can we go home now?

323
00:27:53,839 --> 00:27:58,815
I, I suddenly remembered there's
something urgent at the company.

324
00:27:58,839 --> 00:28:01,136
Then I'll drive you and wait for you.

325
00:28:01,160 --> 00:28:06,399
No need, I can handle
it myself, I'm leaving.

326
00:28:18,519 --> 00:28:21,656
Gang, don't freaking sleep,
play another game with me.

327
00:28:21,680 --> 00:28:26,879
I really can't play anymore. Wu
Suo Wei hasn't come back yet.

328
00:28:27,519 --> 00:28:29,319
What time is it now?

329
00:28:30,319 --> 00:28:32,295
It's twelve o'clock.

330
00:28:32,319 --> 00:28:33,535
That's still early.

331
00:28:33,559 --> 00:28:38,240
All his thoughts are focused on work.

332
00:28:39,799 --> 00:28:41,416
Is your company that busy?

333
00:28:41,440 --> 00:28:48,480
Recently, the business has increased, but
he doesn't need to sleep there every day.

334
00:28:56,200 --> 00:29:02,639
He wouldn't be having an affair in
the office behind your back, would he?

335
00:29:04,119 --> 00:29:10,656
Impossible, he doesn't have the guts.

336
00:29:10,680 --> 00:29:12,696
True.

337
00:29:12,720 --> 00:29:16,856
But he's so handsome,
with bright and shiny eyes.

338
00:29:16,880 --> 00:29:18,680
What about others?

339
00:29:38,839 --> 00:29:41,616
Yes. I think this way
would make it a bit better.

340
00:29:41,640 --> 00:29:43,616
Pretty good, just go with this plan.

341
00:29:43,640 --> 00:29:46,919
Let it be however
comfortable it can be, alright.

342
00:29:49,720 --> 00:29:51,176
Make whom better?

343
00:29:51,200 --> 00:29:54,815
The client is requesting
some modifications.

344
00:29:54,839 --> 00:29:57,639
It was reverted to the first version.

345
00:30:00,440 --> 00:30:02,240
I'll treat you.

346
00:30:03,240 --> 00:30:05,495
Can you come to company today? Okay.

347
00:30:05,519 --> 00:30:07,735
Let's go.

348
00:30:07,759 --> 00:30:10,559
Go to the company, I'll tell you later.

349
00:30:12,519 --> 00:30:17,535
I, I suddenly remembered there's
something urgent at the company.

350
00:30:17,559 --> 00:30:19,856
Then I'll drive you and wait for you.

351
00:30:19,880 --> 00:30:24,720
No need, I can handle
it myself, I'm leaving.

352
00:30:32,720 --> 00:30:35,520
Let's go, catch him cheating.

353
00:30:38,944 --> 00:30:41,159
Quick.

354
00:31:03,960 --> 00:31:06,000
Go die!

355
00:31:15,559 --> 00:31:20,280
Gang, you go over there.

356
00:32:30,039 --> 00:32:33,095
Wow, why are you here?

357
00:32:33,119 --> 00:32:34,696
Can't I come?

358
00:32:34,720 --> 00:32:37,520
Not really.

359
00:32:41,599 --> 00:32:43,399
What is this?

360
00:32:51,680 --> 00:32:54,976
This is an ecological box
I made for Little Jealousy.

361
00:32:55,000 --> 00:32:57,064
The one earlier, made relatively small

362
00:32:57,088 --> 00:32:59,856
due to lack of material.

363
00:32:59,880 --> 00:33:03,136
Now there is enough material,
and the new home is quite large.

364
00:33:03,160 --> 00:33:05,440
I want to give it a new one.

365
00:33:06,559 --> 00:33:08,456
Look, this piece of wood.

366
00:33:08,480 --> 00:33:10,055
This leaf, this wood.

367
00:33:10,079 --> 00:33:11,936
Doesn't the simulated animal skull

368
00:33:11,960 --> 00:33:14,696
look like a mini version
of a tropical rainforest?

369
00:33:14,720 --> 00:33:18,319
According to its species,
it will surely like it.

370
00:33:23,160 --> 00:33:28,176
Are you an idiot? Does it hurt?

371
00:33:28,200 --> 00:33:31,399
No. Just applying a band-aid will be fine.

372
00:33:43,640 --> 00:33:50,159
I was wondering why you've
been so sneaky these days. Sorry.

373
00:33:53,519 --> 00:33:55,319
Sorry.

374
00:33:59,000 --> 00:34:04,616
Chi Cheng, I haven't gotten used
to gay love yet, but I'm quick-witted.

375
00:34:04,640 --> 00:34:07,839
I believe I'll become
a top-notch boyfriend.

376
00:34:10,480 --> 00:34:17,920
You already are.

377
00:34:30,016 --> 00:34:32,879
Adulterer, take this.

378
00:34:42,000 --> 00:34:45,080
It's okay, don't mind him.

379
00:35:18,272 --> 00:35:23,662
♫ I really want to tell you ♫

380
00:35:25,728 --> 00:35:31,665
♫ There's more than just the
sunset and the distant sea ♫

381
00:35:33,024 --> 00:35:39,112
♫ If today won't come back again ♫

382
00:35:39,136 --> 00:35:46,209
♫ Don't mind the change of day and night ♫

383
00:35:47,808 --> 00:35:53,881
♫ I really want to tell you ♫

384
00:35:55,300 --> 00:36:01,265
♫ There's more than
just stars or mountains ♫

385
00:36:02,720 --> 00:36:08,569
♫ The sun rises and
sets, you're all I see ♫

386
00:36:08,593 --> 00:36:16,593
♫ Not fearing the halt of time ♫

387
00:36:17,357 --> 00:36:22,647
♫ The last night on Earth ♫

388
00:36:24,800 --> 00:36:30,542
♫ I just want to confess to you ♫

389
00:36:32,096 --> 00:36:38,105
♫ Get through the doomsday with sincerity ♫

390
00:36:38,129 --> 00:36:46,129
♫ Perhaps no regret ♫

391
00:36:46,944 --> 00:36:52,424
♫ The last night on Earth ♫

392
00:36:54,208 --> 00:36:59,729
♫ When life turns to dust ♫

393
00:37:01,600 --> 00:37:07,609
♫ When seawater kisses the sky ♫

394
00:37:07,633 --> 00:37:15,633
♫ I'll take you away without hesitation ♫
